        "Description": "Rieper the Gold-Gunned Hitman\rCan&#39;t say no to gold on a gun\rAnd if you ever saw them\rYou would even gulp, &quot;I&#39;m done!&quot;\r\rTip: The Shashka A33 Gold is found in the armoury inside Rico&#39;s garage. The El Matador is found in Rico&#39;s safe. The Goldballer is an inventory item players get for completing Hitman 3&#39;s last story map, &quot;Untouchable.&quot;\r\n\r\n<HCCE>",
